summary: okay but the way rdj has been genuinely excited about Brie’s introduction to the MCU and the way he hypes her up constantly, or...
body: okay but the way rdj has been genuinely excited about Brie’s introduction to the MCU and the way he hypes her up constantly, or is a shoulder for her to (literally) cry on - it makes my heart so fucking happy because it’s amazing to see. rdj is so happy for her because moving forward, she’s one of the main faces of the MCU and he knows how that feels (obviously he’s had the last 11 years as experience). and instead of getting any sort of weird animosity towards her, or viewing her as a threat, all I see is a genuine warmth and excitment (like he’s a mentor to her, almost) and i can’t even explain how fantastic it is to see it. i love legends supporting other legends!!!
